s%20studying%20to%20become%20a%20chartered%20accountant.%20Then%20I%20gave%20it%20all%20up%20to%20become%20a%20soft-skills%20trainer.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222468%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20in%20business%20suit%20in%20a%20classroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c339af6fcb546d2d4ce011%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221851%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAkansha%20Jain%2C%2038%2C%20worked%20as%20an%20Chartered%20Accountant%20for%2010%20years%20before%20quitting%20to%20pursue%20soft%20skills.%3Cp%3EAkansha%20Jain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAkansha%20Jain%20spent%206%20years%20studying%20to%20be%20a%20Chartered%20Accountant%20for%20six%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJain%20worked%20as%20an%20accountant%20for%2010%20years%20before%20quitting%20to%20pursue%20a%20passion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20now%20freelances%20as%20a%20soft%20skills%20trainer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fca-akansha-jain-delhi%2Fdetails%2Fexperience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAkansha%20Jain%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20Chartered%20Accountant%20turned%20soft-skills%20training%20freelancer%20based%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%2C%20India.%20This%20essay%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudying%20to%20become%20a%20chartered%20accountant%20was%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20things%20I%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20after%20high%20school%20and%20lasted%20six%20years.%20I%20worked%20hard%20throughout%20the%20process%2C%20studying%20eight%20to%20nine%20hours%20every%20day.%20The%20course%20required%20intelligence%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20persistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20became%20a%20chartered%20accountant%20in%202009.%20I%20spent%20the%20next%2010%20years%20working%20in%20the%20internal%20audit%20departments%20of%20real%20estate%20companies%20and%20auditing%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20had%209-to-5%20jobs.%20But%20my%20commute%2C%20which%20took%20between%2090%20minutes%20and%20two%20hours%2C%20made%20working%20hours%20feel%20a%20lot%20longer.%20I%20left%20home%20at%208%20a.m.%20and%20usually%20only%20got%20back%20by%207%20p.m.%20Coming%20home%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20my%20daughter%20meant%20I%20had%20no%20time%20at%20all%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20time%20I%20was%20doing%20these%20jobs%2C%20there%20was%20something%20missing%20from%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecognizing%20a%20passion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20had%20a%20passion%20for%20public%20speaking%20and%20connecting%20with%20people.%20Even%20before%20I%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20friends%20would%20come%20up%20to%20me%20and%20share%20their%20problems%20with%20me%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20really%20help%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20while%20I%20was%20still%20working%20as%20an%20accountant%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20a%20soft-skills%20course%20from%20a%20cousin%20who%20was%20doing%20the%20program.%20I%20gathered%20up%20all%20my%20courage%20and%20decided%20to%20pursue%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20year%20to%20complete%20the%20program%20because%20I%20was%20juggling%20it%20with%20a%20full-time%20job%20and%20a%20young%20family.%20I%20would%20attend%20in-person%20classes%20two%20times%20a%20week%20after%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20my%20second%20daughter%20in%202020%2C%20and%20knew%20maintaining%20a%20work-life%20balance%20would%20be%20even%20harder%20with%20two%20kids.%20I%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20job%20that%20year%20and%20start%20pursuing%20a%20career%20in%20soft%20skills%2C%20with%20the%20hopes%20of%20starting%20my%20own%20venture.%20Being%20my%20own%20boss%20and%20having%20the%20flexibility%20to%20manage%20my%20children%20became%20a%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20completely%20different%20career%20track%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20worked%20under%20a%20senior%20soft-skills%20trainer%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20tough%20ride.%20There%20is%20no%20connection%20between%20being%20an%20accountant%20and%20a%20soft-skills%20trainer.%20One%20was%20all%20about%20numbers%20and%20auditing.%20The%20other%20focuses%20on%20public%20speaking%2C%20communication%20skills%2C%20and%20body%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20time%20working%20with%20a%20senior%20soft-skills%20trainer%2C%20I%20launched%20my%20own%20business%20called%20Inner%20Spark%20in%202023.%20I%20specialize%20in%20behavioral%20training%20and%20work%20with%20corporations%20to%20design%20and%20lead%20seminars%20on%20leadership%2C%20interpersonal%20skills%2C%20and%20communication.%20One%20of%20my%20favorite%20topics%20is%20emotional%20intelligence%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20the%20most%20essential%20element%20required%20nowadays%2C%20and%20which%20many%20corporations%20today%20still%20lack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20still%20long%20days%20but%20I%20love%20the%20flexibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20my%20own%20business%20came%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges.%20Going%20from%20a%20stable%20monthly%20salary%20to%20not%20knowing%20when%20a%20new%20client%20will%20come%20by%2C%20and%20whether%20I%20will%20earn%20anything%20this%20month%2C%20was%20also%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20drawbacks%2C%20my%20work-life%20balance%20improved%20a%20lot%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20into%20an%20office%20every%20day%2C%20and%20I'm%20able%20to%20give%20my%20kids%20more%20time.%20Work%20on%20some%20days%20is%20just%20self-studying%20for%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20a%20day%20to%20update%20myself%20about%20the%20industry.%20There%20are%20still%20some%20long%20days%20when%20I%20have%20to%20meet%20a%20client%20at%20their%20workplace%2C%20but%20that's%20down%20to%20one%20or%20two%20days%20a%20week%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20currently%20the%20sole%20employee%20of%20the%20company%2C%20but%20I%20hope%20to%20hire%20more%20trainers%20as%20business%20grows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20my%20own%20career%20transition%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hard%20skills%20versus%20soft%20skills%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20one%20is%20more%20important%20than%20the%20other.%20Hard%20skills%20are%20essential%20to%20get%20into%20an%20industry%2C%20but%20for%20continued%20success%20and%20satisfaction%2C%20you%20need%20soft%20skills%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20understand%20your%20own%20and%20others'%20emotions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-accountant-soft-skills-freelancer-entrepreneur-delhi-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707354349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c31e906fcb546d2d4cdf36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-accountant-soft-skills-freelancer-entrepreneur-delhi-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akansha%20Jain%20quit%20her%20dream%20job%20as%20an%20Chartered%20Accountant%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20teaching%20soft%20skills%20and%20being%20her%20own%20boss.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-change-accountant-soft-skills-freelancer-entrepreneur-delhi-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Senate%20bid%20to%20salvage%20Ukraine%20and%20Israel%20aid%20as%20border%20deal%20crumbles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707354175000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FB02A%2Fproduction%