me%20zone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIrvine%20said%20he%20works%20each%20muscle%20group%2C%20but%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20started%20stretching%20daily%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20Irvine%20doesn't%20believe%20in%20rest%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20in%20his%20career%20as%20a%20celebrity%20chef%20and%20star%20of%20multiple%20hit%20Food%20Network%20shows%2C%20which%20involves%20345%20days%20a%20year%20of%20travel%20worldwide.%20And%20certainly%20not%20in%20the%20gym%2C%20where%20the%20trim%2C%20muscular%2058-year-old%20can%20be%20found%20exercising%20at%20all%20hours%2C%20day%20or%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20take%20days%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Irvine%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHealth%20and%20fitness%20has%20been%20a%20staple%20since%20I%20was%2011%20years%20old.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20veteran%20of%20the%20British%20Royal%20Navy%2C%20Irvine%20said%20his%20routines%20combine%20classic%20strength%20exercise%20with%20training%20for%20real-life%20durability%2C%20allowing%20him%20to%20tackle%20feats%20like%20marching%20more%20than%2050%20miles%20across%20Scotland%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20resources%20for%20military%20charities%2C%20a%20focus%20of%20his%20Robert%20Irvine%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%2C%20however%2C%20adjusted%20somewhat%20over%20the%20decades%2C%20at%20least%20to%20incorporate%20daily%20stretching%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-common-gym-injuries-physical-therapist-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeasing%20off%20all-out%20maximum%20lifts%20to%20prevent%20injury%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20doing%20a%20slightly%20different%20routine%20at%2058%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIrvine%20shares%20how%20he%20fits%20in%20workouts%20in%20a%20hectic%20travel%20schedule%2C%20what%20he%20does%20in%20the%20gym%2C%20and%20how%20he's%20training%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanti-aging-exercise-longevity-doctor-peter-attia-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay%20strong%20for%20years%20to%20come%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20follows%20a%20strict%20schedule%20for%20gym%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIrvine%20said%20the%20secret%20to%20his%20consistency%20in%20the%20gym%20is%20simple%20discipline%2C%20making%20the%20time%20to%20fit%20in%20a%20workout%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20time%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20where%20I%20am%2C%20I%20do%20an%20hour-and-a-half%20workout%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20midnight%20or%20three%20in%20the%20morning%20local%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20rest%20days%20are%20advisable.%20Irvine's%20trainer%20encourages%20him%20to%20take%20a%20least%20one%20rest%20day%20a%20week%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20on%20his%20public%20relations%20team%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Irvine%20said%20time%20spent%20on%20a%20plane%20during%20his%20worldwide%20travel%20counts%20as%20rest%2C%20so%20he's%20ready%20to%20hit%20the%20gym%20when%20his%20flight%20lands.%20While%20it%20may%20seem%20grueling%2C%20he%20said%20keeping%20to%20his%20usual%20timing%20helps%20him%20stay%20on%20track%20despite%20being%20constantly%20on%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20I'm%20wired%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20stay%20in%20the%20time%20zone%20I'm%20used%20to%20living%20in%2C%20I%20don't%20change%20my%20routine%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHis%20workouts%20target%20a%20different%20muscle%20group%20each%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIrvine%20follows%20a%20traditional%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkout-split-how-to-tone-body-build-muscle-faster-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody%20part%20workout%20split%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20gym%2C%20dedicating%20a%20separate%20day%20of%20the%20week%20each%20to%20shoulders%2C%20legs%2C%20arms%2C%20back