rofitability%2C%20and%20shrinking%20the%20streaming%20losses%20was%20a%20big%20step%20in%20that%20direction%20that%20should%20help%20pull%20the%20stock%20out%20of%20its%20slump%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Verna%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Insider%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20still%20big%20battles%20ahead%20for%20Disney%20this%20year%20and%20beyond%2C%20but%20today's%20results%20will%20no%20doubt%20bring%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief%20to%20the%20company's%20leaders%20and%20shareholders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDisney%20to%20invest%20in%20%26quot%3BFortnite%26quot%3B%20maker%2C%20announces%20ESPN%20strategy%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBoosting%20the%20results%20were%20a%20slew%20of%20announcements%20reminiscent%20of%20Iger's%20bold%20moves%20during%20his%20first%20tenure%20as%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-fortnite-maker-epic-games-investment-iger-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDisney%20will%20invest%20%241.5%20billion%20into%20Epic%20Games%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20%26quot%3BFortnite.%26quot%3B%20The%20benefits%20of%20the%20partnership%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20be%20twofold%3A%20exposing%20Gen%20Z%20and%20Gen%20Alpha%20%E2%80%94%20age%20groups%20that%20entertainment%20companies%20have%20struggled%20to%20reach%20through%20traditional%20channels%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Disney's%20slate%20of%20IP%2C%20and%20revenue-driving%20through%20in-game%20purchases.%20It's%20a%20move%20geared%20to%20showing%20Wall%20Street%20that%20Disney%20is%20paying%20attention%20to%20gaming%20and%20younger%20demographics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIger%20also%20unveiled%20his%20strategy%20and%20timeline%20for%20bringing%20Disney's%20flagship%20sports%20network%20ESPN%20into%20the%20streaming%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20will%20launch%20a%20stand-alone%20streaming%20service%20with%20ESPN%20and%20its%20sister%20networks%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202025%2C%20something%20Iger%20called%20%26quot%3Binevitable.%26quot%3B%20The%20platform%20will%20likely%20integrate%20betting%20and%20fantasy%2C%20merchandise%2C%20sports%20stats%2C%20and%20customization%2C%20he%20said%20on%20Wednesday's%20earnings%20call.%20Customers%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20bundle%20the%20offering%20with%20Disney%2B%20and%20Hulu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20service%20is%20separate%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-streaming-app-disney-warner-fox-pay-cable-tv-nfl-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esuper%20sports%20streamer%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20coming%20this%20fall%2C%20which%20the%20company%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20will%20combine%20ESPN%20and%20ABC's%20sports%20programming%20with%20Fox%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery's.%20Iger%20described%20the%20joint%20venture%20as%20a%20multi-channel%20play%20to%20attract%20new%20customers%20who%20may%20think%20the%20classic%20pay-TV%20bundle%20is%20too%20expensive.%20The%20companies%20haven't%20yet%20announced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-questions-espn-fox-and-wbd-new-sports-streamer-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eprice%20for%20their%20streamer%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Wall%20Street%20is%20curious%20how%20quickly%20these%20new%20efforts%20could%20cannibalize%20and%20replace%20Disney's%20existing%20linear%20TV%20business%20that%20relies%20on%20the%20cable%20bundle%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20Disney%20will%20balance%20investment%20and%20priorities%20between%20the%20two%20sports%20streamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20there's%20consumer%20demand%2C%20the%20JV%20faces%20several%20hurdles%2C%20from%20challenges%20brought%20by%20existing%20distributors%20to%20antitrust%20opposition%2C%20LightShed%20Partners%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20published%20ahead%20of%20Disney's%20earnings%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Iger%20had%20been%20under%20pressure%20from%20investors%20to%20better%20monetize%20and%20define%20the%20future%20of%20its%20sports%20network%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20cord-cutting%20and%20rising%20sports-rights%20costs.%20Some%20had%20even%20called%20for%20Disney%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia-telecom%2Fdisney-ceo-chapek-rejects-activist-loebs-call-espn-spin-off-ft-2022-09-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Espin%20off%20the%20ESPN%20brand%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Challenges%20aside%2C%20the%20new%20sports%20streaming%20strategy%20is%20a%20big%20step%20forward%20for%20Iger%20and%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMoana%26quot%3B%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20may%20be%20Disney's%202024%20MVPs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIger%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20concert%20movie%20%26quot%3BTaylor%20Swift%3A%20The%20Eras%20Tour%26quot%3B%20will%20exclusively%20stream%20on%20Disney%2B.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20film%20of%20the%20record-breaking%20tour%20has%20garnered%20more%20than%20%24260%20million%20at%20the%20global%20box%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20regarding%20other%20films%20and%20TV%2C%20Iger%20took%20a%20much%20sunnier%20tone%20than%20during%20November's%20earnings%20call%20when%20he%20acknowledged%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbob-iger-admits-disney-movies-have-been-bad-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edrop%20in%20quality%20of%20Disney%20films%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20great%20about%20where%20we%20are%20with%20the%20studio%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%3Cspan%3En%20our%20zeal%20to%20greatly%20increase%20volume%2C%20partially%20tied%20to%20wanting%20to%20chase%20more%20global%20subs%20for%20our%20streaming%20platform%2C%20some%20of%20our%20studios%20lost%20a%20little%20focus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20a%20strategy%20that%20included%20reducing%20output%2C%20including%20from%20Marvel%3B%20killing%20films%20and%20series%20that%20didn't%20meet%20a%20quality%20benchmark%3B%20and%20doubling%20down%20on%20a%20pipeline%20of%20movies%20the%20studio%20believes%20will%20succeed.%20He%20pointed%20to%20an%20upcoming%20theatrical%20film%20sequel%20to%20%26quot%3BMoana%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20should%20give%20the%20box%20office%20a%20boost%20after%20last%20year's%20lackluster%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20there%20will%20still%20be%20detractors%2C%20but%20Iger%20didn't%20seem%20concerned%2C%20particularly%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20company%20will%20dole%20out%20a%20dividend%20of%20%240.45%20per%20share%20in%20July%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%2050%25%20increase%20from%20the%20one%20paid%20out%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeltz's%20Trian%20didn't%20sound%20immediately%20impressed.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu%20all%20over%20again.%20We%20saw%20this%20movie%20last%20year%20and%20we%20didn't%20like%20the%20ending%2C%26quot%3B%20Trian%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Iger%20told%20CNBC%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20last%20thing%20that%20we%20need%20right%20now%20is%20to%20be%20distracted%20in%20terms%20of%20our%20time%2C%20our%20energy%2C%20by%20an%20activist%20or%20activists%20that%2C%20frankly%2C%20have%20a%20completely%20different%20agenda%20and%20don't%20understand%20our%20company%2C%20its%20assets%2C%20even%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20Disney%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20it%20came%20to%20another%20known%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-twitter-jeff-bezos-mark-zuckerberg-iger-criticize-fight-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIger%20critic%2C%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20earlier%20this%20week%20said%20he%20would%20finance%20%26quot%3BMandalorian%26quot%3B%20actor%20Gina%20Carano's%20lawsuit%20against%20Disney%2C%20Iger's%20feathers%20also%20didn't%20seem%20ruffled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20simply%20when%20a