2%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20states%20will%20be%20supporting%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20opposing%20views%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20leader%20of%20opposition%20Yashpal%20Arya%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20should%20have%20been%20given%20some%20time%20to%20prepare%20to%20debate%20before%20passing%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20haste%20behind%20implementing%20it%3F%20We%20have%20sufficient%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20expect%20us%20to%20read%20such%20a%20lengthy%20document%2C%20which%20was%20submitted%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20ago%2C%20and%20start%20the%20discussion.%20It%20looks%20like%20the%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20hide%20something%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20full%20majority%20to%20pass%20the%20Bill%2C%20but%20it%20would%20have%20been%20better%20to%20give%20the%20Opposition%20some%20time%20to%20prepare%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20government%20formed%20the%20Justice%20Ranjana%20Prakash%20Desai%20Committee%20to%20develop%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%20However%2C%20despite%20submitting%20its%20report%20within%2013%20months%2C%20the%20committee%20did%20not%20publicly%20disclose%20its%20blueprint%20or%20engage%20with%20social%20groups%20or%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20this%20lack%20of%20transparency%20prevented%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20from%20providing%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20party%20wrote%20letters%20to%20the%20committee%20twice%2C%20asking%20for%20the%20draft%2C%20but%20the%20committee%20did%20not%20give%20any%20reply.%20In%20a%20country%20where%20many%20laws%2C%20including%20criminal%20laws%2C%20are%20still%20not%20uniform%2C%20how%20can%20anyone%20give%20their%20views%20on%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20imagination%20only%3F%20If%20the%20committee%20had%20given%20a%20blueprint%2C%20many%20practical%20and%20valuable%20ideas%20would%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20come%20to%20light%20through%20the%20press%20that%20your%20law%20is%20a%20Bill%20brought%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20providing%20gender%20equality%20to%20women.%20If%20so%2C%20then%20why%20are%20you%20keeping%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20women%20of%20Uttarakhand%20away%20from%20this%20equality%20right%3F%20Were%20the%20women%20belonging%20to%204%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20not%20entitled%20to%20your%20so-called%20gender%20equality%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B8%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B6%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%88%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%A0%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A5%A4%2013%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B8%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%AA%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%80%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%