2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fantony-blinken-meets-with-israeli-pm-netanyahu%2Famp_articleshow%2F107497920.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Muslims%20Targeted%20in%20128%20Demolitions%2C%20617%20People%20Affected'%3A%20Amnesty%20Reports%20on%20Bulldozer%20Action%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20International%20human%20rights%20organisation%20Amnesty%20International%20has%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20cessation%20of%20the%20widespread%20and%20unlawful%20demolitions%20of%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20businesses%2C%20and%20places%20of%20worship%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20released%20two%20reports%20on%20Wednesday%20(February%207)%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20speak%20up%2C%20your%20house%20will%20be%20demolished%E2%80%99%3A%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Unearthing%20Accountability%3A%20JCB%E2%80%99s%20Role%20and%20Responsibility%20in%20Bulldozer%20Injustice%20in%20India%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20document%20the%20punitive%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20properties%20in%20at%20least%20five%20states%20using%20JCB-branded%20bulldozers%20calling%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20hate%20campaign%20against%20the%20minority%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgn%C3%A8s%20Callamard%2C%20Amnesty%20International%E2%80%99s%20Secretary%20General%20expressed%20deep%20concern%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20unlawful%20demolition%20of%20Muslim%20properties%20by%20the%20Indian%20authorities%2C%20peddled%20as%20%E2%80%98bulldozer%20justice%2C%E2%80%99%20is%20cruel%20and%20appalling.%20Such%20displacement%20and%20dispossession%20are%20deeply%20unjust%2C%20unlawful%2C%20and%20discriminatory.%20They%20are%20destroying%20families%20and%20must%20stop%20immediately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20urged%20the%20government%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20halt%20the%20de%20facto%20policy%20of%20demolishing%20people%E2%80%99s%20homes%20as%20a%20form%20of%20extra-judicial%20punishment%20and%20ensure%20nobody%20is%20made%20homeless%20as%20a%20result%20of%20forced%20evictions%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20press%20note%2C%20adding%20that%20adequate%20compensation%20is%20given%20to%20all%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20demolitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fthe-unconstitutionality-of-bulldozer-justice%5C%22%3EThe%20Unconstitutionality%20of%20%E2%80%98Bulldozer%20Justice%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20investigations%2C%20between%20April%20and%20June%202022%2C%20authorities%20in%20five%20states%20carried%20out%20demolitions%20as%20a%20form%20of%20%E2%80%98punishment%E2%80%99%20following%20communal%20violence%20or%20protests%20against%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20detail%20128%20documented%20demolitions%2C%20with%20at%20least%2033%20instances%20of%20JCB%E2%80%99s%20equipment%20being%20repeatedly%20used%2C%20affecting%20617%20individuals%20who%20were%20rendered%20homeless%20or%20deprived%20of%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20reported%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpunitive%20demolitions%E2%80%9D%20at%2056%2C%20the%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20demolitions%2C%20often%20enacted%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20removing%20illegal%20construction%2C%20violated%20due%20process%20outlined%20in%20domestic%20and%20international%20human%20rights%20law.%20They%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Muslim-concentrated%20localities%20were%20targeted%2C%20while%20Muslim-owned%20properties%20were%20selectively%20demolished%2C%20leaving%20nearby%20Hindu-owned%20properties%20untouched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20not%20the%20only%20vehicles%20used%2C%20JCB%20bulldozers%20have%20become%20the%20brand%20of%20choice%2C%20with%20the%20company%20earning%20nicknames%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Jihadi%20Control%20Board%E2%80%99%20from%20right-wing%20media%20and%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20International%20had%20earlier%20written%20to%20JCB%20regarding%20the%20matter.%20In%20response%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20they%20had%20no%20control%20or%20responsibility%20over%20how%20its%20products%20are%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%20Guiding%20Principles%20on%20Business%20and%20Human%20Rights%2C%20JCB%20has%20a%20responsibility%20to%20respect%20human%20rights%20and%20conduct%20due%20diligence%20to%20identify%2C%20prevent%2C%20and%20mitigate%20adverse%20human%20rights%20impacts%20linked%20to%20its%20operations%2C%20the%20human%20rights%20group%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20international%20standards%2C%20JCB%20is%20responsible%20for%20addressing%20what%20third-party%20buyers%20do%20with%20its%20equipment.%20The%20company%20must%20stop%20looking%20away%20as%20JCB%20machines%20are%20used%20to%20target%20and%20punish%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20while%20people%20sloganeer%20anti-Muslim%20vitriol%20mounted%20from%20atop%20these%20bulldozers.%20JCB%20cannot%20continue%20to%20evade%20responsibility%20while%20its%20machines%20are%20repeatedly%20used%20to%20inflict%20human%20rights%20abuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20Callamard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707314020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F16172609%2FUntitled-design-2021-07-16T172559.085.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-targeted-in-128-demolitions-617-people-affected-amnesty-reports-on-bulldozer-action%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP-ruled%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20reported%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpunitive%20demolitions%E2%80%9D%20at%2056%2C%20the%20report%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslims-targeted-in-128-demolitions-617-people-affected-amnesty-reports-on-bulldozer-action%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20Lies%20Low%2C%20Rumours%20Rife%20on%20Aunt-Nephew%20Tension%20Within%20TMC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07162042%2FTMC-collage.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20looming%20large%2C%20whispers%20of%20internal%20discord%20within%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20are%20growing%20louder.%20At%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20speculation%20lies%20the%20relationship%20between%20party%20supremo%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20nephew%2C%20the%20perceived%20heir%20apparent%2C%20Abhishek%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbhishek%E2%80%99s%20low%20profile%20fuels%20rumours%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20six%20weeks%2C%20Abhishek%20has%20maintained%20a%20noticeably%20low%20profile%2C%20primarily%20limiting%20his%20activities%20to%20his%20own%20constituency%2C%20Diamond%20Harbour.%20While%20he%20did%20participate%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fram-temple-mamata-banerjee-modi%5C%22%3EMamata%E2%80%99s%20interfaith%20%E2%80%98Sanhati%20Yatra%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20his%20conspicuous%20absence%20from%20the%20ongoing%20protest%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20against%20the%20denial%20of%20funds%20to%20the%20state%20has%20further%20fuelled%20rumours%20of%20a%20rift%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20absence%20is%20particularly%20striking%20given%20Mamata%E2%80%99s%20personal%20commitment%20to%20the%20dharna%20in%20Kolkata.%20Despite%20instructions%20for%20all%20party%20MPs%20to%20participate%2C%20Abhishek%20remained%20in%20Delhi%20for%20parliamentary%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20serving%20his%20constituency%20actively%2C%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fmptrack%2F17-lok-sabha%2Fabhishek-banerjee%5C%22%3Eparliamentary%20engagement%20remains%20low%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20attendance%20record%20reflects%20this%2C%20standing%20at%2014%25%20compared%20to%20the%20national%20average%20of%2079%25%2C%20and%20participation%20in%20two%20debates%20versus%20the%20national%20average%20of%2045.1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20distance%20from%20the%20dharna%2C%20despite%20senior%20leaders%20joining%20Mamata%20to%20spend%20multiple%20nights%20at%20the%20campsite%2C%20suggests%20a%20power%20struggle%20or%20a%20difference%20in%20strategies%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClash%20with%20the%20old%20guard%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tensions%20initially%20started%20in%202022%2C%20when%20two%20conflicting%20candidate%20lists%20surfaced%20for%20the%20municipal%20polls.%20One%20list%20was%20backed%20by%20party%20veterans%20Partha%20Chatterjee%20and%20Subrata%20Bakshi%2C%20and%20the%20other%20made%20by%20I-PAC%2C%20patronised%20by%20Abhishek.%20Mamata%20initially%20endorsed%20the%20Chatterjee-Bakshi%20list%20but%20faced%20challenges%20from%20Abhishek%2C%20who%20overruled%20her%20in%20several%20municipalities%20and%20favoured%20I-PAC-recommended%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20discord%20led%20to%20discontent%20among%20senior%20leaders%20like%20Chatterjee%20and%20Bakshi%2C%20who%20even%20threatened%20to%20step%20down.%20Caught%20between%20the%20old%20guard%20and%20rising%20aspirations%2C%20Mamata%20dissolved%20key%20party%20committees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20national%20general%20secretary%20position.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20later%20reinstated%2C%20solidifying%20his%20prominence%20and%20his%20de%20facto%20No.%202%20status%20within%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Abhishek%20has%20been%20advocating%20for%20a%20possible%20retirement%20age%20for%20politicians%2C%20mirroring%20practices%20in%20other%20sectors.%20This%20further%20ruffled%20feathers%20among%20seasoned%20party%20members%2C%20who%20perceiving%20it%20as%20a%20veiled%20message%20targeting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20drew%20closer%2C%20the%20debate%20resurfaced.%20Senior%20leaders%20like%20Subrata%20Bakshi%2C%20Firhad%20Hakim%20and%20Sudip%20Bandopadhyay%20expressed%20differing%20views.%20While%20Bakshi%20openly%20encouraged%20Abhishek%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20Hakim%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20younger%20leaders%20learning%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20history.%20Bandopadhyay%E2%80%99s%20comment%20about%20potential%20chaos%20after%20Mamata%E2%80%99s%20departure%20further%20fuelled%20speculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20a%20counter-offensive%20from%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20camp%2C%20with%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20advocating%20for%20retiring%20older%20leaders%20and%20promoting%20younger%2C%20tech-savvy%20individuals.%20While%20officially%2C%20Abhishek%20claimed%20to%20be%20an%20%E2%80%9Cobedient%20soldier%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20reiterated%20his%20position%20on%20the%20age%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20there%20is%20a%20certain%20age%20of%20retirement%20for%20every%20sector%2C%20it%20should%20be%20the%20same%20for%20politics%20as%20well.%20Yes%2C%20I%20said%20that%2C%20but%20what%20is%20wrong%20with%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20declared%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20was%20became%20inadvertently%20swept%20into%20the%20discourse%2C%20as%20there%20were%20questions%20about%20whether%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20indirectly%20targeted%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20public%20rally%2C%20she%20announced%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20believe%20in%20showing%20the%20door%20to%20anyone%20who%20reaches%20the%20age%20of%2060.%E2%80%9D%20This%20statement%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20her%20policy%20of%20utilising%20experienced%20bureaucrats%20beyond%20retirement%2C%20was%20interpreted%20by%20political%20observers%20as%20a%20message%20of%20confidence%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cold%20guard%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20implicit%20rebuke%20to%20those%20proposing%20an%20age%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20struggle%20or%20strategic%20difference%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20just%20before%20the%20panchayat%20poll%2C%20Abhishek%20undertook%20a%20mass%20outreach%20programme%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Nabo%20Jowar%20Yatra%E2%80%99%2C%20crisscrossing%20the%20state%20for%2051%20days%20with%20road%20shows%20and%20public%20meetings.%20While%20he%20is%20largely%20credited%20with%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20the%20panchayat%20poll%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20party%20remained%20hesitant%20to%20accept%20his%20growing%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20panchayat%20election%2C%20securing%2051%25%20of%20votes%20and%20winning%20all%20districts%2C%20was%20not%20without%20controversy.%20There%20was%20widespread%20violence%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20over%2050%20lives.%20The%20opposition%20raised%20allegations%20of%20the%20party%20using%20government%20resources%20and%20undue%20influence%20from%20Block%20Development%20Officers%20(BDOs)%20to%20sway%20the%20results.%20Over%20a%20thousand%20legal%20cases%20challenging%20the%20election%E2%80%99s%20legitimacy%20have%20been%20filed%20in%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20within%20the%20party%2C%20accustomed%20to%20Mamata%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20view%20the%20party%20as%20synonymous%20with%20her.%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20selection%20of%20candidates%20based%20on%20vote%20count%2C%20alleged%20ballot%20rigging%20and%20formation%20of%20his%20own%20youth-led%20teams%20during%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20sparked%20criticism%20and%20accusations%20of%20sidelining%20established%20members.%20Abdul%20Karim%20Choudhury%2C%20the%20TMC%20MLA%20of%20Islampur%20in%20North%20Dinajpur%2C%20openly%20rebelled%20and%20fielded%20independent%20candidates%20against%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20official%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20should%20not%20have%20been%20given%20so%20much%20responsibility.%20He%20does%20not%20understand%20anything%20about%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Choudhury%2C%20taking%20a%20potshot%20at%20Abhishek.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20again%20become%20inactive%20if%20one%20particular%20leader%20tries%20to%20control%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20cousin%20Aditi%20Gayen%20wrote%20a%20cryptic%20social%20media%20post%2C%20hinting%20at%20a%20potential%20difference%20within%20the%20family.%20Gayen%20has%20been%20actively%20sharing%20numerous%20posts%20and%20reposts%20related%20to%20Abhishek%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20noticeable%20absence%20of%20any%20reposts%20featuring%20the%20party%20supremo%20on%20her%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22bn%5C%22%3E%E0%A6%AF%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%20%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%B0%E0%A6%BE%20%E0%A6%B8%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A5%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%A8%20%E0%A6%AA%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%20%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BE%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E0%A6%85%E0%A6%AF%E0%A7%8B%E0%A6%97%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%20%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%95%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A4%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%A6%E0%A7%87%E0%A6%B0%20%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%BF%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%E0%A7%87%20%E0%A6%98%E0%A6%B0%20%E0%A6%B8%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%9C%E0%A6%BE%E0%A6%AF%E0%A6%BC%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Aditi%20Gayen%20(%40AditiG_Official)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAditiG_Official%2Fstatus%2F1753722095601881152%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Mamata%C2%A0%20abruptly%20cancelled%20her%20scheduled%20Delhi%20trip%2C%20citing%20budget-related%20responsibilities.%20A%20section%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fmamata-banerjee-scraps-delhi-trip-cites-state-budget-related-responsibilities%2Fcid%2F1998563%5C%22%3EKolkata%20media%20is%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20is%20due%20to%20her%20reluctance%20to%20share%20a%20roof%20with%20Abhishek%2C%20as%20she%20typically%20prefers%20to%20stay%20at%20his%20official%20residence%20during%20her%20visits%20to%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficially%20though%2C%20the%20party%20is%20denying%20any%20possibility%20of%20a%20rift%20between%20the%20aunt-nephew%20duo.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CAbhishek%20Banerjee%20is%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20could%20not%20take%20part%20in%20the%20Kolkata%20dharna.%20Even%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20did%20not%20attend%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20dharna%20a%20few%20months%20back%20over%20the%20same%20demand.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20always%20that%20one%20has%20to%20be%20present%20to%20show%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20clarified%20Trinamool%20Youth%20Congress%20leader%20Sayani%20Ghosh%2C%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20political%20analyst%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EBengal%20Conundrum%3A%20The%20Rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Future%20of%20the%20TMC%3C%2Fem%3E%20Sambit%20Pal%20echoed%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20were%20a%20rift%2C%20Mamata%20would%20have%20taken%20drastic%20actions%2C%20such%20as%20removing%20Abhishek%2C%20and%20would%20not%20remain%20silent%20when%20spokespersons%20like%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20constantly%20attack%20senior%20leaders.%20It%20appears%20that%20Mamata%20is%20aligning%20herself%20with%20the%20veteran%20leaders%2C%20but%20she%20is%20also%20signalling%20that%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20has%20control%20over%20the%20organisation%20by%20not%20taking%20any%20action%20against%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20times%2C%20several%20senior%20leaders%20have%20openly%20pledged%20their%20allegiance%20towards%20Mamata%2C%20indicating%20a%20fissure%20within%20the%20organisation.%20Abhishek%2C%20backed%20by%20I-PAC%2C%20attempted%20to%20revamp%20the%20organisation%20and%20build%20his%20own%20loyal%20base%2C%20but%20his%20efforts%20have%20seemingly%20resulted%20in%20the%20emergence%20of%20two%20distinct%20factions%20across%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbhishek%20is%20still%20overseeing%20the%20organisation%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20attempting%20to%20manage%20it%20more%20corporately%20by%20removing%20senior%20leaders%20and%20avoiding%20any%20sympathetic%20sentiments.%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20to%20step%20forward%20to%20resolve%20the%20discontent%20between%20the%20senior%20and%20junior%20members%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDipak%20Adhikari%2C%20the%20actor-turned-MP%20widely%20known%20as%20Dev%2C%20has%20stepped%20just%20down%20from%20all%20governmental%20roles%20in%20his%20constituency.%20Speculation%20is%20rife%20within%20the%20political%20circles%20of%20Kolkata%20about%20the%20potential%20defection%20of%20another%20veteran%20should%20he%20be%20denied%20tickets%20in%20the%20upcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%202021%20election%20victory%2C%20the%20TMC%20has%20faced%20a%20barrage%20of%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20impacting%20its%20image.%20The%20arrest%20of%20former%20education%20minister%20Partha%20Chatterjee%20and%20seizure%20of%20crores%20in%20cash%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20detention%20of%20party%20heavyweight%20Anubrata%20Mondal%20and%20his%20daughter%20in%20a%20cattle%20scam%2C%20have%20jolted%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20arrest%20of%20state%20minister%20Jyoti%20Priya%20Mallick%20and%20a%20series%20of%20raids%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20have%20further%20rattled%20the%20party.%20Mallick%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20strength%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20due%20to%20his%20influence%20in%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20Adding%20to%20the%20woes%2C%20Abhishek%20himself%20faces%20investigation%20for%20money%20laundering.%20This%20relentless%20onslaught%20of%20corruption%20cases%2C%20coupled%20with%20internal%20strife%20over%20succession%2C%20has%20left%20many%20party%20insiders%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20preparedness%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20still%20maintain%20that%20there%20is%20no%20coordination%20within%20the%20party%20in%20my%20district.%20Whatever%20you%20call%20it%2C%20young%20or%20old%2C%20there%20is%20no%20coordination%20between%20the%20team.%20You%20know%20how%20many%20times%20I%20have%20said%20this%20upstairs.%20If%20Congress%20and%20CPM%20fight%20together%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20we%20will%20have%20a%20tough%20battle.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20I-PAC%20isn%E2%80%99t%20working%20in%20full%20swing%20this%20time%20like%20in%20other%20elections%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20doing%20surveys%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20outspoken%20MLA%20Humayun%20Kabir%20from%20Murshidabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20political%20observers%20are%20still%20putting%20the%20TMC%20ahead%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%20%E2%80%93%20the%20three%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty%20predicts%20a%20strong%20showing%20for%20the%20TMC%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20between%20their%20tactics%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20success%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Trinamool%20Party%20stands%20on%20a%20few%20pillars%20like%20the%20BJP.%20The%20pillars%20are%20Beneficiary%2C%20Religious%20Vote%2C%20Administration%2C%20Money%20and%20Muscle%20Power.%20Trinamool%20is%20the%20second%20richest%20party%20after%20BJP%20and%20gets%20massive%20electoral%20bonds.%20They%20fight%20elections%20on%20these%20pillars.%20They%20will%20do%20much%20better%20than%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20does%20not%20want%20the%20party%20to%20divide%20along%20these%20lines%20before%20the%20crucial%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Mamata%20knows%2C%20as%20does%20Abhishek%2C%20that%20people%20will%20vote%20for%20her%20regardless%20of%20the%20election.%20She%20is%20the%20sole%20face%20of%20the%20TMC%2C%E2%80%9D%20summed%20up%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Bengali%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707312633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07162042%2FTMC-collage.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-abhishek-banerjee-lays-low-rumours-rife-on-aunt-nephew-tension-within-tmc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhishek's%20distance%20from%20Mamata's%20dharna%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20despite%20senior%20leaders%20joining%20the%20CM%20to%20spend%20multiple%20nights%20at%20the%20campsite%2C%20suggests%20a%20power%20struggle%20or%20a%20difference%20in%20strategies%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-abhishek-banerjee-lays-low-rumours-rife-on-aunt-nephew-tension-within-tmc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20in%20Russia%20sleeps%20with%20husband's%20mummified%20corpse%20for%204%20years%2C%20engages%20in%20occult%20rituals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707312537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107496912%2Cimgsize-19336.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwoman-in-ru