of%20uncertainty%20over%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20suitability%20to%20play%20Tests%20looks%20incredibly%20na%C3%AFve%20now.%20His%20lengths%20adjust%20seamlessly%20the%20moment%20he%20switches%20between%20formats%2C%20his%20conventional%20swing%20is%20just%20as%20sharp%20as%20anyone%E2%80%99s%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20lethal%20when%20the%20ball%20starts%20to%20reverse%2C%20and%20that%20awkward%20angle%20of%20release%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20point%20of%20difference%20since%20it%20never%20allows%20the%20batters%20to%20leave%20him%20on%20line%20with%20any%20real%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20no%20further%20than%20England%E2%80%99s%20Joe%20Root%20in%20the%20first%20two%20Tests%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20media%20murmur%2C%20India%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20resorted%20to%20hostile%20pitches%20straightaway%20and%20instead%20showed%20faith%20in%20the%20depth%20of%20their%20bowling%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Root%20walked%20in%20to%20bat%20in%20England%E2%80%99s%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20opening%20Test%20at%20Hyderabad%2C%20the%20pitch%20was%20beautifully%20paced%20to%20put%20on%20a%20big%20score.%20But%20a%20sharp%20in-ducker%20from%20Bumrah%20is%20the%20last%20thing%20one%20wants%20to%20face%20at%20the%20start%20of%20his%20innings.%20Root%20was%20beaten%20on%20the%20inside%20edge%20and%20caught%20plumb%20in%20front%20of%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20really%20have%20mattered%20when%20he%20came%20out%20to%20bat%20on%20day%20two%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Vizag.%20The%20pitch%20was%20again%20nicely%20paced%20but%20Rohit%20Sharma%20wasted%20no%20time%20and%20threw%20the%20ball%20to%20Bumrah.%20With%20reverse%20swing%20on%20offer%2C%20Bumrah%20kept%20tempting%20Root%20on%20playing%20at%20one%20outside%20his%20off-stump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoot%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20budge%20easily%20but%20the%20amount%20of%20doubt%20Bumrah%20creates%20in%20a%20batter%E2%80%99s%20head%20becomes%20impossibly%20hard%20to%20negate.%20Root%20let%20two%20go%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKhurdra72916%2Fstatus%2F1753693792014922079%5C%22%3Epoked%20at%20the%20third%20one%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20ball%20that%20breached%20his%20defence%20at%20Hyderabad%20ought%20to%20have%20played%20on%20his%20mind.%20He%20simply%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20allowed%20for%20that%20to%20repeat.%20Well%2C%20he%20succeeded%20at%20that%20but%20only%20to%20edge%20at%20one%20leaving%20him%20and%20furnish%20an%20easiest%20of%20grabs%20to%20the%20first%20slip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20dismissals%20are%20an%20ode%20to%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20manufacture%20wickets%20on%20surfaces%20not%20particularly%20conducive%20to%20fast%20bowling.%20But%20Bumrah%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20showboating%20just%20yet.%20What%20followed%20Root%E2%80%99s%20dismissal%20at%20Vizag%20is%20hands%20down%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20series%20so%20far%20and%20in%20all%20likelihood%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20topped%20for%20the%20three%20remaining%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOllie%20Pope%2C%20England%E2%80%99s%20fidgety%20middle%20order%20rookie%2C%20never%20quite%20looks%20at%20ease%20in%20the%20middle.%20But%20he%E2%80%99d%20proved%20to%20be%20India%E2%80%99s%20unexpected%20nemesis%20in%20their%20defeat%20in%20the%20first%20Test.%20At%20Vizag%20too%2C%20he%E2%80%99d%20been%20off%20to%20a%20shaky%20start%20and%20was%20just%20about%20surviving%20while%20looking%20like%20getting%20out%20every%20other%20ball.%20Until%20Bumrah%20decided%20to%20end%20his%20struggle%20once%20and%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20things%20in%20cricket%20match%20the%20aesthetics%20of%20a%20reverse%20swinging%20yorker%20of%20surgical%20precision.%20It%20feels%20so%20rewarding%20to%20watch.%20It%E2%80%99s%20reel%20material.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20bowler%20announcing%20he%E2%80%99s%20in%20charge%20and%20that%20the%20batter%20is%20nothing%20more%20than%20an%20expendable%20pawn%20in%20this%20game.%