%20comes%20close%20to%20him.%20Factor%20in%20his%20ridiculous%20output%20in%20the%20shorter%20formats%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20quite%20possibly%20looking%20at%20a%20bowler%20of%20the%20rarest%20possible%20breed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20being%20the%20easiest%20on%20the%20eye%20has%20deferred%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20elevation%20to%20being%20regarded%20as%20a%20bona%20fide%20legend%20of%20this%20sport.%20It%20takes%20time%20for%20years%20and%20years%20of%20bias%20and%20conditioning%20to%20wear%20off.%20Our%20eyes%20are%20trained%20to%20view%20great%20fast%20bowlers%20a%20certain%20way%20and%20Bumrah%20looks%20like%20none%20of%20those%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdjectives%20like%20%3Cem%3Ejaffa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epeach%3C%2Fem%3E%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20thrown%20as%20leniently%20to%20describe%20his%20deliveries%20as%20they%E2%80%99d%20be%20for%20a%20bowler%20with%20a%20more%20traditional%20action%20who%20looked%20the%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMust%20be%20the%20angle%20the%20batsmen%20struggle%20to%20pick%20for%20the%20time%20being.%E2%80%99%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98These%20anomalies%20are%20eventually%20found%20out.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98They%20always%20are.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20of%20time.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20the%20anomaly%20never%20stopped.%20Beating%20the%20batter%20on%20either%20edge%2C%20lifting%20the%20ball%20unusually%20off%20the%20length%2C%20setting%20up%20a%20gorgeously%20deceptive%20slower%20one%2C%20or%20throwing%20in%20the%20sucker-punch%20with%20a%20searing%20yorker%2C%20Bumrah%E2%80%99s%20repertoire%20sets%20him%20apart%20from%20any%20of%20his%20contemporaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20the%20discipline%20and%20persistence%20to%20repeatedly%20bowl%20into%20the%20channel%20and%20induce%20mistakes%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20possesses%20the%20weapons%20to%20relentlessly%20attack%20when%20he%20wants%20to.%20This%20allows%20him%20to%20minimise%20the%20prize%20of%20the%20tradeoff%20between%20accuracy%20and%20intent.%20He%20takes%20his%20wickets%20conceding%20the%20fewest%20runs%2C%20taking%20fewer%20balls%20than%20most%2C%20and%20manages%20to%20not%20leak%20easy%20runs%20in%20the%20process.%20He%20strikes%20the%20impossible%20balance%20between%20average%2C%20strike%20rate%2C%20and%20economy%20rate.%20Once%20again%2C%20among%20active%20fast%20bowlers%2C%20only%20Pat%20Cummins%20rivals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstats.espncricinfo.com%2Fci%2Fengine%2Fstats%2Findex.html%3Fbowling_pacespin%3D1%3Bclass%3D1%3Bfilter%3Dadvanced%3Borderby%3Dbowling_average%3Bqualmin1%3D100%3Bqualval1%3Dwickets%3Bspanmin1%3D1%2BJan%2B2018%3Bspanval1%3Dspan%3Btemplate%3Dresults%3Btype%3Dbowling%5C%22%3Ethese%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20spent%20nearly%20a%20whole%20year%20away%20from%20cricket%20and%20only%20just%20managed%20to%20be%20ready%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20last%20year.%20That%20back%20has%20long%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20kryptonite.%20Former%20greats%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fmy-problem-with-him-michael-holding-reveals-what-makes-jaspit-bumrah-injury-prone%2Fstory-G1brLvqw1cc0VSjtX5C6HI.html%5C%22%3EMichael%20Holding%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fjasprit-bumrah-s-action-isn-t-sustainable-if-i-was-there-i-d-have-told-him-shoaib-akhtar-blames-india-for-mismanagement-101679393639252.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAkhtar%2520suggested%2520that%2520for%2520Bumrah%2Cmatches%2520will%2520prolong%2520his%2520career.%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20expressed%20concern%20over%20his%20action%20that%20they%20think%20forces%20him%20to%20expend%20too%20much%20shoulder%20strength%20to%20generate%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20year-long%20absence%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20out%20of%20order%20to%20wonder%20whether%20he%E2%80%99d%20ever%20return%20the%20same%20bowler%20he%20once%20was.%20Well%2C%20