Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20north%F0%9F%93%8D%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGazaStrip%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23GazaStrip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20destruction%20and%20loss%20is%20staggering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20footage%20shows%20one%20of%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%20health%20centres.%20There%20is%20nothing%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20unprecedented%20level%20of%20destruction%20and%20forced%20displacement%2C%20taking%20place%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fz1el0QfhEe%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fz1el0QfhEe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UNRWA%20(%40UNRWA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUNRWA%2Fstatus%2F1754530324783239532%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20has%20said%20that%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20wounded%20or%20are%20missing%20in%20Gaza%20since%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20post-October%207%20military%20action%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707292803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07123556%2FGFp2Hp1WoAA3117.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-secretary-general-appoints-independent-panel-to-examine-unrwas-operations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20reports%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20Israel%20has%20not%20provided%20any%20evidence%20linking%20UNRWA%20personnel%20to%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-secretary-general-appoints-independent-panel-to-examine-unrwas-operations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Videocon-ICICI%20Bank%20Loan%20Case%3A%20Bombay%20HC%20Declares%20Arrest%20of%20Chanda%20Kochhar%2C%20Husband%20'Illegal'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07120934%2FEffect-2024-02-07T120925.773.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Bombay%20high%20court%20has%20ruled%20the%20arrest%20of%20Chanda%20Kochhar%2C%20former%20managing%20director%20and%20chief%20executive%20officer%2C%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Deepak%20Kochhar%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20connection%20with%20Videocon%20loan%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Anuja%20Prabhudessai%20and%20Justice%20N.R.%20Borkar%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20February%206%2C%20upheld%20a%20previous%20order%20by%20the%20same%20court%20but%20by%20a%20different%20bench.%20The%20high%20court%20in%20an%20interim%20order%20passed%20in%20January%202023%20had%20granted%20the%20duo%20bail%20soon%20after%20their%20arrest.%20The%20Kochhars%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20in%20December%202022%20in%20what%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20Videocon-ICICI%20Bank%20loan%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20their%20arrest%2C%20they%20moved%20the%20court%20challenging%20their%20arrest%20and%20sought%20it%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D.%20On%20January%209%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20passed%20its%20interim%20order%20which%20not%20only%20granted%20them%20bail%20but%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20CBI%20for%20making%20the%20arrest%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccasual%20and%20mechanical%E2%80%9D%20manner%20without%20application%20of%20mind%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbombay-high-court-says-arrest-of-chanda-kochhar-her-husband-in-icici-bank-videocon-loan-case-illegal%2Fcid%2F1998774%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20Kochhars%2C%20the%20CBI%20had%20also%20arrested%20Videocon%20group%20founder%20Venugopal%20Dhoot%20in%20the%20case.%20He%2C%20too%2C%20was%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20high%20court%20in%20January%202023%20in%20its%20interim%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20the%20Kochhars%20is%20that%20ICICI%20Bank%20had%20sanctioned%20credit%20facilities%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%203%2C250%20crore%20to%20Videocon%20Group%20companies%2C%20promoted%20by%20Dhoot%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Banking%20Regulation%20Act%2C%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20guidelines%2C%20and%20credit%20policy%20of%20the%20private%20sector%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20filed%20in%20the%20case%20in%202019%2C%20the%20CBI%20named%20Chanda%20Kochhar%2C%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20and%20Dhoot%20along%20with%20Nupower%20Renewables%20(NRL)%2C%20managed%20by%20Deepak%20Kochhar%2C%20Supreme%20Energy%2C%20Videocon%20International%20Electronics%20Ltd%20and%20Videocon%20Industries%20Ltd%20as%20accused.%20The%20FIR%20was%20filed%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20sections%20related%20to%20criminal%20conspiracy%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20also%20alleged%20that%20in%20an%20act%20of%20%3Cem%3Equid%20pro%20quo%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Dhoot%20made%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2064%20crore%20in%20Nupower%20Renewables%20through%20Supreme%20Energy%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(SEPL)%2C%20and%20transferred%20SEPL%20to%20Pinnacle%20Energy%20Trust%20managed%20by%20Deepak%20Kochhar%20through%20a%20circuitous%20route%20between%202010%20and%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707291048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F07120934%2FEffect-2024-02-07T120925.773.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fvideocon-icici-bank-loan-case-bombay-hc-declares-arrest-of-chanda-koc