t%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20Guwahati%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20was%20solved%20swiftly%20before%20the%20accused%20could%20fly%20half%20a%20thousand%20kilometres%20away%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandip%20Suresh%20Kambli%2C%2042%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20last%20afternoon%20at%20the%20Azara%20hotel%20near%20Guwahati%20airport.%20The%20accused%20-%20Anjali%20Shaw%2C%2025%2C%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20Rakesh%20Shaw%2C%2027%20-%20were%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20to%20Kolkata%20later%20in%20the%20night%2C%20but%20prompt%20police%20action%20led%20to%20their%20arrest%20before%20they%20could%20reach%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKambli%2C%20a%20car%20dealer%20from%20Pune%2C%20was%20first%20spotted%20by%20hotel%20staff%20lying%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20his%20room%2C%20bleeding%20profusely%20from%20his%20nose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20a%20restaurant%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20airport%2C%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Kambli%2C%20who%20she%20had%20befriended%20at%20the%20airport%20last%20year%2C%20said%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20led%20to%20complications%20since%20Anjali%20was%20already%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Rakesh%2C%20who%20had%20been%20pressurising%20her%20to%20marry%20him.%20What%20complicated%20the%20issue%20further%20was%20that%20the%20victim%20had%20intimate%20pictures%20with%20her%20on%20his%20phone%2C%20Anjali%20said%20during%20her%20interrogation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20the%20couple%20-%20Anjali%20and%20Rakesh%20-%20to%20devise%20a%20plan%20to%20confront%20Kambli%20over%20those%20photos.%20They%20had%20earlier%20planned%20to%20meet%20at%20the%20Kolkata%20airport%2C%20but%20Kambli%20moved%20it%20to%20Guwahati%2C%20where%20he%20booked%20a%20room%20in%20the%20five-star%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20flew%20to%20Guwahati%20together%20but%20parted%20their%20ways%20on%20reaching%20Guwahati.%20Rakesh%20had%20even%20booked%20a%20room%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20same%20hotel%20without%20Kambli's%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20their%20plan%2C%20Anjali%20was%20joined%20by%20Kambli%20in%20the%20city%20and%20they%20checked%20in%20at%20the%20hotel%20together%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Rakesh%20arrived%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20meeting%2C%20Rakesh's%20arrival%20enraged%20Kambli%20and%20a%20fight%20erupted%20between%20the%20two.%20The%20fight%20left%20Kambli%20injured%2C%20seeing%20which%20the%20couple%20fled.%20They%20also%20took%20away%20two%20mobile%20phones%20belonging%20to%20Kambli%20-%20which%20allegedly%20had%20their%20intimate%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20phone%20call%20from%20Rakesh%20later%20in%20the%20day%20alerted%20the%20hotel%20authorities%20and%20they%20informed%20the%20Guwahati%20city%20police.%20The%20cops%20promptly%20went%20through%20the%20hotel%20register%2C%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20and%20airport%20passengers'%20list%20to%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20two%20suspects.%20Anjali%20and%20Rakesh%20were%20arrested%20near%20the%20hotel%20before%20they%20could%20board%20the%209%3A15%20pm%20flight%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20remains%20under%20investigation%20as%20the%20cops%20are%20trying%20to%20piece%20together%20the%20events%20that%20led%20to%20their%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707206400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frjidfu38_guwahati-airport_625x300_20_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fguwahati-news%2Flove-triangle-ends-in-guwahati-murder-over-intimate-pics-solved-in-hours-5004009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20love%20triangle%20ended%20in%20a%20brutal%20murder%20at%20a%20five-star%20hotel%20in%20Guwahati%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20was%20solved%20swiftly%20before%20the%20accused%20could%20fly%20half%20a%20thousand%20kilometres%20away%20to%20Kolkata.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fguwahati-news%2Flove-