flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Comprehensive%20data%20on%20water%20quantity%20and%20timings%2C%20enhancing%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20DC%20Sunkara%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20IoT%20system%20has%20already%20been%20successfully%20implemented%20in%2063%20OHTs%20in%2050%20habitations%20in%20Erode%20district%2C%20resulting%20in%20significant%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20reduced%20motor%20running%20time%2C%20lower%20electricity%20bills%2C%20and%20minimised%20water%20wastage.%20More%20importantly%2C%20the%20reliability%20of%20water%20supply%20to%20the%20public%20has%20seen%20a%20remarkable%20improvement%3B%20thus%20alleviating%20the%20burden%20on%20women%20who%20often%20spend%20considerable%20time%20waiting%20near%20taps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20initiative%20costs%20roughly%20Rs%201%20to%201.5%20lakh%20per%20OHT%2C%20and%20has%20been%20mostly%20taken%20up%20under%20the%20village%20panchayat%20general%20fund%20or%2015th%20Central%20Finance%20Commission%20(CFC)%20funds.%20After%20the%20initial%20successes%2C%20we%20are%20working%20on%20installing%20it%20in%20150%20OHTs%20in%20Har%20Ghar%20Jal%20villages%20(all%20households%20in%20that%20village%20are%20provided%20with%20tap%20water%20supply)%20using%20these%20funds%20along%20with%20the%20District%20Mineral%20Foundation%20funds%2C%20Corporate%20Environment%20Responsibility%20funds%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Residents%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20Erode%20are%20dependent%20on%20the%20OHT%20water%20supply%20system.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.25-1706793757.j