nued%20making%20these%20reels%20using%20his%20broken-down%20phone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20August%202023%2C%20I%20began%20learning%20how%20to%20make%20reels.%20See%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20an%20introverted%20person%20and%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20much%20to%20people.%20Making%20these%20reels%20was%20a%20way%20for%20me%20to%20further%20my%20self-confidence.%20In%20my%20village%2C%20there%20was%20no%20one%20that%20I%20could%20speak%20to%20in%20English%2C%20particularly%20with%20that%20accent.%20There%20were%20some%20%5BIndian%5D%20people%20I%20studied%20with%20whom%20I%20only%20spoke%20in%20Hindi%20because%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20normal%20speaking%20to%20them%20in%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Dhiraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStarting%20out%2C%20I%20would%20listen%20to%20native%20speakers%20of%20English%20and%20then%20record%20that%20in%20my%20voice.%20I%20would%20record%20myself%20speaking%20like%20a%20native%20English%20speaker%20every%20single%20day.%20I%20would%20then%20compare%20my%20recordings%20with%20how%20native%20English%20speakers%20spoke%20online.%20Initially%2C%20it%20felt%20very%20strange.%20However%2C%20over%20time%2C%20I%20could%20notice%20improvements%20in%20the%20way%20I%20spoke%20English.%20After%20doing%20this%20for%20six%20months%20consistently%2C%20I%20could%20see%20real%20improvements%20and%20started%20to%20make%20reels.%20Seeing%20this%20improvement%20motivated%20me%20further%20to%20continue%20making%20reels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20August%20to%20October%202023%2C%20Dhiraj%20barely%20made%20four%20reels.%20From%20mid-October%20onwards%2C%20he%20began%20posting%20more%20regularly%20on%20Instagram.%20In%20the%20following%20month%2C%20he%20began%20making%20and%20posting%20one%20reel%20per%20day.%20All%20the%20growth%20we%20see%20in%20his%20follower%20count%20on%20Instagram%20today%20began%20in%20December%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20August%20to%20a