E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC0ts_FSPs9t%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Dhiraj%20Takri%20(%40dhirajtakri)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20gained%20about%2010%2C000%20followers%2C%20my%20brother%20ordered%20a%20phone%20and%20camera%20for%20me.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20phone%20and%20camera%20were%20delivered%20home%2C%20my%20follower%20count%20had%20risen%20to%20about%20300%2C000.%20I%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20learnt%20how%20to%20operate%20a%20camera.%20I%20use%20my%20phone%20to%20make%20all%20my%20videos%20(reels).%20It%20takes%20a%20little%20time%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20operate%20a%20camera%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20reels%20I%E2%80%99ve%20posted%20on%20IG%20have%20been%20shot%20in%20my%20village%20and%20on%20my%20Motorola%20Moto%20G40%20smartphone.%20However%2C%20in%20making%20these%20reels%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20broken%20the%20screen%20but%20decided%20to%20not%20change%20or%20replace%20it%20since%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20I%20will%20buy%20a%20new%20phone%20once%20I%20have%20the%20money%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20negativity%20%26amp%3B%20fame%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20when%20Dhiraj%20Takri%20started%20making%20reels%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20getting%20a%20single%20comment.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20first%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20he%20received%20many%20hateful%20and%20tasteless%20comments%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20also%20went%20on%20for%20only