%20had%20a%20team%20prepared%20below%20with%20blankets%20and%20nets%20ready%20in%20case%20the%20kidnappers%20tried%20to%20throw%20the%20boy%20off%20the%20balcony.%20At%20this%20crucial%20juncture%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20send%20the%20suspect%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20suspect%20Nitin%20proceeded%20to%20ring%20the%20bell%2C%20but%20the%20moment%20his%20accomplice%20opened%20the%20door%20he%20sensed%20that%20something%20was%20wrong%20and%20tried%20to%20shut%20it%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20he%20was%20about%20to%20shut%20the%20door%2C%20I%20told%20one%20of%20my%20officers%20that%20we%20had%20to%20break%20these%20doors%20down.%20Luckily%2C%20there%20was%20a%20little%20gap%20on%20top%20of%20the%20iron%20grill%20door.%20One%20of%20my%20officers%20was%20able%20to%20bend%20the%20iron%20grill%20part%20of%20the%20door%20down%20and%20that%20left%20enough%20space%20for%20me%20to%20enter.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20inside%20began%20firing%20at%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20As%20per%20news%20reports%2C%20a%20bullet%20hit%20Inspector%20Vinay%20Tyagi%E2%80%99s%20vest%2C%20while%20another%20hit%20commando%20Kuldip%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20this%20chaos%2C%20Dr%20Naik%20climbed%20over%20the%20bent%20iron%20grill%20and%20took%20a%20peek%20at%20the%20gap%20left%20behind%20by%20a%20second%20wooden%20door%20inside%20to%20see%20if%20the%20child%20was%20inside%20the%20main%20hall%20of%20the%20flat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20found%20that%20the%20boy%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20there.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20ordered%20the%20personnel%20behind%20me%20to%20fire%20back.%20There%20was%20an%20exchange%20of%20fire.%20One%20of%20the%20kidnappers%20was%20shot%20down%20on%20the%20ground%20lying%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%20while%20the%20other%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20leg.%20My%20team%20immediately%20followed%20me%20inside%20while%20I%20went%20straight%20to%20the%20bedroom%20to%20find%20the%20child%20under%20a%20blanket%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20the%20child%20was%20terrified%20following%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire%20outside.%20%E2%80%9CI%20slowly%20took%20down%20the%20blanket%20and%20told%20him%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Beta%2C%20mein%20police%20uncle%20hoon.%20Mein%20tumhare%20papa%20ke%20paas%20le%20jaane%20ke%20liye%20aaya%20hoon.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20After%20hearing%20those%20words%2C%20he%20immediately%20jumped%20off%20the%20bed%20and%20hugged%20me.%20I%20carried%20him%20out%20of%20the%20flat%20covering%20his%20eyes.%20As%20we%20were%20driving%20to%20GTB%20Hospital%2C%20I%20called%20up%20his%20father%20and%20told%20him%20that%20we%20had%20rescued%20his%20child%20safely.%20This%20was%20around%202%20am%20in%20the%20wee%20hours%20%5Bof%206%20February%202018%5D.%20The%20father%20was%20asleep%20when%20we%20called%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20among%20the%20other%20two%20suspects%20inside%20the%20flat%2C%20one%20was%20killed%20while%20the%20other%20was%20injured.%20The%20police%20personnel%20injured%20by%20gunshots%20were%20saved%20by%20their%20bulletproof%20vests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20made%20our%20way%20to%20GTB%20Hospital.%20After%20the%20doctor%20on%20duty%20confirmed%20that%20the%20child%20had%20not%20suffered%20any%20serious%20injuries%20or%20abuse%2C%20the%20parents%20took%20him%20into%20their%20arms.%20It%20was%20an%20emotional%20moment%20seeing%20these%20tearful%20parents%20reuniting%20with%20their%20son.%20I%20also%20shed%20a%20tear.%20Four%20officers%2C%20including%20me%2C%20received%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Police%20Medal%20for%20Gallantry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20life%20of%20a%20police%20officer%20has%20its%20share%20of%20controversy%20and%20disappointments%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20moments%20like%20these%20that%20make%20the%20journey%20worth%20it.%20Seeing%20that%20tearful%20reunion%20between%20the%20parents%20and%20their%20son%2C%20%E2%80%9Cand%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20made%20it%20possible%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20what%20makes%20this%20path%20worth%20it.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dr%20Ram%20Gopal%20Naik%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsyimza%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%2FImran%20Zahid%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706536707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FSnapinsta.app_408791019_1441618009726504_8932941298547774044_n_1080-1706533714.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Ram%20Gopal%20Naik%2C%20a%20doctor-turned-IPS%20officer%2C%20has%20many%20achievements%20in%20his%20name.%20Awarded%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Police%20Medal%20for%20Gallantry%20after%20rescuing%20a%20five-year-old%2C%20the%20Hindi-film%20industry%20has%20also%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20movie%20inspired%20by%20his%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339947%2Fips-officer-doctor-ram-gopal-naik-biopic-bollywood-film-on-life-clearing-upsc-civil-services-exam%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Legendary%20Places%20in%20Mumbai%20For%20the%20Best%20Pav%20Bhaji%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20it%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20the%20spicy%2C%20buttery%20flavours%20of%20the%20quintessential%20%3Cem%3Epav%20bhaji%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20your%20growing-up%20years.%20This%20street%20food%20has%2C%20for%20aeons%20now%2C%20been%20synonymous%20with%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20i